k\\\" data-v-df02a584><span class=\\\"logo-icon\\\" data-v-df02a584>🏛️</span><span class=\\\"logo-text\\\" data-v-df02a584>Diagimmo<strong data-v-df02a584>Marchés</strong></span></div><div class=\\\"visual-overlay\\\" data-v-df02a584>Visiter le site</div></div><div class=\\\"project-info\\\" data-v-df02a584><div class=\\\"tags\\\" data-v-df02a584><span class=\\\"tag\\\" data-v-df02a584>Projet Client</span><span class=\\\"tag outline\\\" data-v-df02a584>Web Premium</span></div><h3 data-v-df02a584>Diagimmo Marchés</h3><p class=\\\"project-desc\\\" data-v-df02a584><strong data-v-df02a584>Les marchés publics du diagnostic immobilier en un clic.</strong><br data-v-df02a584> Trouvez facilement des missions de diagnostics immobiliers (DPE, amiante, plomb, etc.) et restez informé des nouvelles opportunités. </p></div></a></div></section><section class=\\\"bottom-cta fade-in-up\\\" style=\\\"animation-delay:0.6s;\\\" data-v-df02a584><div class=\\\"cta-glass-panel\\\" data-v-df02a584><div class=\\\"cta-glow\\\" data-v-df02a584></div><h2 data-v-df02a584>Prêt à passer à l&#39;échelle supérieure ?</h2><p data-v-df02a584>Confiez-moi vos défis techniques. Je m&#39;occupe de construire la solution qui fera la différence.</p><a href=\\\"mailto:amineitji@gmail.com\\\" class=\\\"btn-glow large mt-4\\\" data-v-df02a584><span class=\\\"btn-content\\\" data-v-df02a584>Contacter Amine</span></a></div></section>\", 4);\nexport function render(_ctx, _cache, $props, $setup, $data, $options) {\n  const _component_router_link = _resolveComponent(\"router-link\");\n  return _openBlock(), _createElementBlock(\"div\", _hoisted_1, [_hoisted_2, _hoisted_3, _hoisted_4, _createElementVNode(\"header\", _hoisted_5, [_createElementVNode(\"div\", _hoisted_6, [_createElementVNode(\"div\", _hoisted_7, [_hoisted_8, _createElementVNode(\"div\", _hoisted_11, [_hoisted_12, _createVNode(_component_router_link, {\n    to: \"/projets\",\n    class: \"btn-outline\"\n  }, {\n    default: _withCtx(() => [_createText