s=\"logo-text\">Diag<strong>ERP</strong></span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"visual-overlay\">Visiter l'application</div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"project-info\">\n            <div class=\"tags\"><span class=\"tag\">SaaS B2B</span><span class=\"tag outline\">Co-fondateur</span></div>\n            <h3>DiagERP</h3>\n            <p class=\"project-desc\">\n              <strong>Efficace, Rapide, Professionnel.</strong> Votre Etat des Risques en toute simplicité.\n              En quelques secondes et en ligne, obtenez l'Etat des Risques (ERP + ENSA) d'un bien. Ce document essentiel informe les acquéreurs et locataires des risques d'un bien immobilier.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n\n        <a href=\"https://diagimmomarches.fr\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"project-glass-card\">\n          <div class=\"project-logo-container immo-logo-bg\">\n            <div class=\"logo-mark\">\n              <span class=\"logo-icon\">🏛️</span>\n              <span class=\"logo-text\">Diagimmo<strong>Marchés</strong></span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"visual-overlay\">Visiter le site</div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"project-info\">\n            <div class=\"tags\"><span class=\"tag\">Projet Client</span><span class=\"tag outline\">Web Premium</span></div>\n            <h3>Diagimmo Marchés</h3>\n            <p class=\"project-desc\">\n              <strong>Les marchés publics du diagnostic immobilier en un clic.</strong><br>\n              Trouvez facilement des missions de diagnostics immobiliers (DPE, amiante, plomb, etc.) et restez informé des nouvelles opportunités.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"bottom-cta fade-in-up\" style=\"animation-delay: 0.6s;\">\n      <div class=\"cta-glass-panel\">\n        <div class=\"cta-glow\"></div>\n        <h2>Prêt à passer à l'échelle supérieure ?</h2>\n        <p>Confiez-moi vos défis techniques. Je m'occupe de construire la solution qui fera la différence.</p>\n        <a href=\"mailto:amineitji@gmail.com\" class=\"btn-glow large mt-4\">\n          <span class=\"btn-content\">Contacter Amine</span>\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script>\nexport default {\n  name: 'HomePage'\n};\n</script>\n\n<style scoped>\n/* ==========================================================================\n   VARIABLES & THEME GLOBAL\n   ========================================================================== */\n:root {\n  --color-bg: #030712; /* Noir bleuté profond */\n  --color-card: rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.4);\n  --color-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);\n  \n  --text-main: #f9fafb;\n  --text-muted: #9ca3af;\n  \n  --primary-blue: #3b82f6;\n  --primary-purple: #8b5cf6;\n  --primary-cyan: #06b6d4;\n  \n  --transition-smooth: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);\n}\n\n.innovative-layout {\n  background-color: var(--color-bg);\n  color: var(--text-main);\n  min-height: 100vh;\n  position: relative;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;\n  line-height: 1.6;\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   ARRIÈRE-PLAN ANIMÉ (Grille + Blobs)\n   ========================================================================== */\n.bg-grid {\n  position: absolute;\n  inset: 0;\n  background-image: \n    linear-gradient(to right, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),\n    linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);\n  background-size: 40px 40px;\n  mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, black 20%, transparent 100%);\n  -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, black 20%, transparent 100%);\n  z-index: 0;\n  pointer-events: none;\n}\n\n.blob {\n  position: absolute;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  filter: blur(120px);\n  opacity: 0.4;\n  z-index: 0;\n  pointer-events: none;\n  animation: float 20s ease-in-out infinite alternate;\n}\n.blob-blue {\n  top: -10%; left: -10%;\n  width: 600px; height: 600px;\n  background: var(--primary-blue);\n}\n.blob-purple {\n  bottom: 20%; right: -10%;\n  width: 500px; height: 500px;\n  background: var(--primary-purple);\n  animation-delay: -5s;\n}\n\n@keyframes float {\n  0% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }\n  100% { transform: translate(50px, 50px) scale(1.1); }\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   GÉNÉRIQUE (Sections, Boutons, Titres)\n   ========================================================================== */\nheader, section {\n  position: relative;\n  z-index: 1;\n  max-width: 1200px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  padding: 0 24px;\n}\n\n.section-heading {\n  margin-bottom: 40px;\n}\n.section-heading h2 {\n  font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);\n  font-weight: 700;\n  letter-spacing: -0.02em;\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\n}\n.section-heading p {\n  color: var(--text-muted);\n  font-size: 1.1rem;\n}\n\n/* Bouton principal avec Glow effect */\n.btn-glow {\n  position: relative;\n  display: inline-flex;\n  border-radius: 100px;\n  padding: 2px; /* Espace pour le gradient */\n  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-blue), var(--primary-purple), var(--primary-cyan));\n  background-size: 200% auto;\n  animation: gradientShift 3s linear infinite;\n  text-decoration: none;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  transition: transform 0.2s ease;\n}\n.btn-glow:hover {\n  transform: scale(1.02);\n  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.4);\n}\n.btn-content {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  background: #0f172a;\n  color: white;\n  padding: 12px 28px;\n  border-radius: 100px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  width: 100%;\n  transition: background 0.3s ease;\n}\n.btn-glow:hover .btn-content {\n  background: transparent;\n}\n.btn-glow.large .btn-content { padding: 16px 40px; font-size: 1.1rem; }\n\n/* Bouton secondaire */\n.btn-outline {\n  display: inline-flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  padding: 14px 28px;\n  border-radius: 100px;\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);\n  color: var(--text-main);\n  font-weight: 600;\n  text-decoration: none;\n  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n  transition: var(--transition-smooth);\n}\n.btn-outline:hover {\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n  border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n}\n\n@keyframes gradientShift {\n  0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }\n  100% { background-position: 200% 50%; }\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   1. HERO SECTION\n   ========================================================================== */\n.hero {\n  padding-top: 140px;\n  padding-bottom: 80px;\n}\n.hero-container {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 60px;\n}\n.hero-content {\n  flex: 1.2;\n}\n\n/* Badge Statut \"Pulsing\" */\n.badge-wrapper { margin-bottom: 24px; }\n.status-badge {\n  display: inline-flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 12px;\n  padding: 8px 16px;\n  border-radius: 100px;\n  background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05);\n  border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);\n  color: #34d399;\n  font-size: 0.85rem;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  position: relative;\n}\n.pulse-dot {\n  width: 8px; height: 8px;\n  background: #10b981;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  position: relative;\n  z-index: 2;\n}\n.pulse-ring {\n  position: absolute;\n  left: 12px; /* Ajusté par rapport au padding */\n  width: 16px; height: 16px;\n  background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.5);\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  animation: pulseAnim 2s cubic-bezier(0.215, 0.61, 0.355, 1) infinite;\n  z-index: 1;\n}\n@keyframes pulseAnim {\n  0% { transform: scale(0.5); opacity: 1; }\n  100% { transform: scale(2.5); opacity: 0; }\n}\n\n.hero-title {\n  font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);\n  line-height: 1.1;\n  font-weight: 800;\n  margin-bottom: 24px;\n  letter-spacing: -0.03em;\n}\n.animated-gradient-text {\n  background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-blue), var(--primary-purple), var(--primary-cyan), var(--primary-blue));\n  background-size: 200% auto;\n  -webkit-background-clip: text;\n  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n  animation: gradientShift 4s linear infinite;\n}\n\n.hero-description {\n  font-size: 1.15rem;\n  color: var(--text-muted);\n  max-width: 600px;\n  margin-bottom: 40px;\n}\n.hero-description strong { color: white; }\n.hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }\n\n/* Image avec bordure animée (Conic Gradient) */\n.hero-visual {\n  flex: 1;\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: flex-end;\n}\n.animated-border-box {\n  position: relative;\n  width: 100%;\n  max-width: 480px; /* Grande photo */\n  aspect-ratio: 4/5;\n  border-radius: 30px;\n  padding: 4px; /* Épaisseur de la bordure animée */\n  overflow: hidden;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n}\n.animated-border-box::before {\n  content: '';\n  position: absolute;\n  width: 150%;\n  height: 150%;\n  background: conic-gradient(transparent, transparent, transparent, var(--primary-blue), var(--primary-purple));\n  animation: rotateBorder 4s linear infinite;\n}\n.inner-image-wrapper {\n  position: relative;\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 100%;\n  border-radius: 26px; /* Doit être légèrement inférieur à la box mère */\n  overflow: hidden;\n  background: #000;\n  z-index: 1;\n}\n.inner-image-wrapper img {\n  width: 100%; height: 100%;\n  object-fit: cover;\n}\n@keyframes rotateBorder {\n  0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }\n  100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   2. SOCIAL PROOF (Logos Glassmorphism)\n   ========================================================================== */\n.trust-bar {\n  margin-bottom: 100px;\n}\n.trust-label {\n  text-align: center;\n  font-size: 0.75rem;\n  letter-spacing: 0.15em;\n  color: var(--text-muted);\n  margin-bottom: 24px;\n}\n.trust-logos {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: center;\n  gap: 24px;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n}\n.glass-logo {\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);\n  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);\n  padding: 12px 24px;\n  border-radius: 100px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;\n}\n.glass-logo .dim { color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.9rem;}\n.emoji { font-size: 1.2rem; }\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   3. SERVICES BENTO BOX\n   ========================================================================== */\n.services-bento {\n  margin-bottom: 120px;\n}\n.bento-grid {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n  gap: 24px;\n}\n.bento-card {\n  position: relative;\n  background: var(--color-card);\n  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);\n  border-radius: 30px;\n  padding: 40px;\n  backdrop-filter: blur(16px);\n  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);\n  transition: var(--transition-smooth);\n  overflow: hidden;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n}\n\n/* Effet 3D Hover */\n.bento-card:hover {\n  transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.01);\n  border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);\n  box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\n}\n\n.span-1 { grid-column: span 1; }\n.span-2 { grid-column: span 2; }\n.span-3 { grid-column: span 3; }\n\n/* Icônes */\n.icon-wrapper {\n  width: 50px; height: 50px;\n  border-radius: 14px;\n  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\n  margin-bottom: 24px;\n}\n.icon-wrapper svg { width: 24px; height: 24px; }\n.ai-theme { background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2); color: #a78bfa; }\n.web-theme { background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2); color: #60a5fa; }\n.data-theme { background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2); color: #34d399; }\n\n/* Carte IA Spéciale */\n.highlight-card .card-header {\n  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start;\n}\n.tech-tag {\n  background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(139,92,246,0.2), transparent);\n  border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.3);\n  color: #c4b5fd;\n  padding: 6px 12px;\n  border-radius: 100px;\n  font-size: 0.8rem;\n}\n.card-glow {\n  position: absolute;\n  top: -50px; right: -50px;\n  width: 200px; height: 200px;\n  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(139,92,246,0.3) 0%, transparent 70%);\n  filter: blur(30px);\n  pointer-events: none;\n}\n\n.bento-card h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }\n.bento-card p { color: var(--text-muted); }\n\n.horizontal-card {\n  flex-direction: row; align-items: center; gap: 32px;\n}\n.horizontal-card .icon-wrapper { margin-bottom: 0; flex-shrink: 0; width: 60px; height: 60px; }\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   4. PROJECTS SECTION (Avec les Logos et Nouveaux Textes)\n   ========================================================================== */\n.work-section {\n  margin-bottom: 120px;\n}\n.projects-grid {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n  gap: 32px;\n}\n.project-glass-card {\n  display: block;\n  text-decoration: none;\n  background: var(--color-card);\n  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);\n  border-radius: 30px;\n  padding: 24px;\n  backdrop-filter: blur(16px);\n  transition: var(--transition-smooth);\n}\n.project-glass-card:hover {\n  transform: translateY(-5px);\n  border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\n}\n\n/* Logos Générés en Code */\n.project-logo-container {\n  height: 220px;\n  border-radius: 20px;\n  margin-bottom: 24px;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  position: relative;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  transition: var(--transition-smooth);\n}\n.erp-logo-bg {\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59,130,246,0.1), rgba(139,92,246,0.05));\n  border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.15);\n}\n.immo-logo-bg {\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(16,185,129,0.1), rgba(6,182,212,0.05));\n  border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.15);\n}\n\n/* Le macaron du logo au centre */\n.logo-mark {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 12px;\n  background: rgba(3, 7, 18, 0.7);\n  padding: 16px 32px;\n  border-radius: 100px;\n  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);\n  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n  transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);\n}\n.project-glass-card:hover .logo-mark {\n  transform: scale(1.08); /* Zoom du logo au survol */\n}\n\n.logo-icon {\n  font-size: 1.8rem;\n}\n.logo-text {\n  font-size: 1.5rem;\n  font-weight: 300;\n  color: white;\n  letter-spacing: -0.02em;\n}\n.logo-text strong {\n  font-weight: 800;\n}\n\n/* Overlay au survol */\n.visual-overlay {\n  position: absolute; inset: 0;\n  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);\n  backdrop-filter: blur(4px);\n  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\n  color: white; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1rem;\n  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px);\n  transition: var(--transition-smooth);\n}\n.project-glass-card:hover .visual-overlay {\n  opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0);\n}\n\n.project-info { padding: 0 8px; }\n.tags { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px; }\n.tag { font-size: 0.75rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 100px; font-weight: 500; color: #e5e7eb;}\n.tag.outline { background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); color: var(--text-muted); }\n\n.project-info h3 { color: white; font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }\n.project-desc { \n  color: var(--text-muted); \n  font-size: 1rem; \n  line-height: 1.6;\n}\n.project-desc strong {\n  color: var(--text-main);\n  font-weight: 600;\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   5. BOTTOM CTA\n   ========================================================================== */\n.bottom-cta {\n  margin-bottom: 80px;\n}\n.cta-glass-panel {\n  position: relative;\n  background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(30,41,59,0.5), rgba(3,7,18,0.8));\n  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);\n  border-radius: 40px;\n  padding: 80px 40px;\n  text-align: center;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);\n}\n.cta-glow {\n  position: absolute;\n  top: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);\n  width: 600px; height: 300px;\n  background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2) 0%, transparent 60%);\n  pointer-events: none;\n}\n.cta-glass-panel h2 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px; position: relative;}\n.cta-glass-panel p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative;}\n.mt-4 { margin-top: 32px; }\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   ANIMATIONS D'ENTRÉE (Fade In Up)\n   ========================================================================== */\n.fade-in-up {\n  opacity: 0;\n  transform: translateY(30px);\n  animation: fadeInUpAnim 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;\n}\n@keyframes fadeInUpAnim {\n  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   RESPONSIVE DESIGN\n   ========================================================================== */\n@media (max-width: 1024px) {\n  .hero-container { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }\n  .hero-content { align-items: center; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }\n  .hero-actions { justify-content: center; }\n  .hero-visual { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }\n  \n  .bento-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n  .span-1, .span-2, .span-3 { grid-column: span 1; }\n  .horizontal-card { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; text-align: left; gap: 16px;}\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n  .hero-title { font-size: 2.5rem; }\n  .projects-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n  .cta-glass-panel { padding: 40px 20px; }\n  .cta-glass-panel h2 { font-size: 2rem; }\n}\n</style>"],"mappings